<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَضْلِ اللَّهِ}</span> ... رِزْقِ اللهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَهْوًا}</span> ... مَا يُلْهِي مِنْ غِنَاءٍ، وَزِينَةٍ، وَنَحْوِهِمَا.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>